                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9366" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0610</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1164 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一架飞机起落背后的六百人：海航技术西北维修基地的领航者计划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The 600 Behind Every Takeoff and Landing： HNA Technik Northwest Maintenance Base&#39;s  &quot;Pioneer Plan&quot; </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈琳，李传进，李飞，赵龙峰，许轲然</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航航空技术有限公司西北维修基地</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">31 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">培训与开发；人力资源管理；师徒制度；人才梯队；高精尖维修</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Training and Development; Human resource management; Mentoring System; Talent Echelon; High Precision Maintenance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航技术西北维修基地（以下简称“西北维修基地”）成立于2010年，是海航技术九大维修基地之一。西北维修基地积极探索人力资源培训与开发新模式，优化维修人才体系结构，探索出高精尖维修行业人才培训新路径。西北维修基地建设过程中识别出其人才培养存在培训目标不明确、培训安排不系统、实践转化能力差、监督反馈机制不明的实际缺陷。本案例以海航技术西北维修基地“领航者计划”进行人力资源培训与开发为对象，明晰培训与开发中的管理思想，探究其如何通过培训与开发流程建立良好宏大的人才梯队资源结构，维系各高精尖业务维修模块的安全、高效运转，打造企业人力资源培训与开发科学化建设路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">HNA Technology Northwest Maintenance Base (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Northwest Maintenance Base&quot;) was established in 2010, is one of the nine major maintenance bases of HNA technology. Northwest Maintenance Base actively explores a new model of human resources training and development, optimizes the system structure of maintenance talents, and explores a new path for personnel training in the high-precision maintenance industry. In the process of construction of Northwest maintenance base, it is identified that there are some actual defects in personnel training, such as unclear training objectives, unsystematic training arrangements, poor practice transformation ability and unclear supervision and feedback mechanism. This case takes the human resources training and development of the &quot;Pilot Program&quot; in the HNA Technology Northwest Maintenance Base as the object, clarify the management ideas in training and development, explore how to establish a good and grand talent echelon resource structure through the training and development process, and maintain the safe and efficient operation of each sophisticated business maintenance module. Create a scientific construction path for enterprise human resources training and development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《培训与开发》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">培训与开发；师徒制度；人才梯队建设理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
